This religious Christmas card features three photos along with the Bible verse from Luke 2:14 in a handwritten style. This three photo Christian Christmas card is perfect for sending meaningful holiday greetings. The type on the front is green and the back in a matching green with white dots. There is room for two square photos and one vertical. This original card by Lea Delaveris Design is part of a collection and can be found in other colors as well.
